T +7)</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Địa điểm</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Trực tuyến qua Google Meet hoặc Zoom (sẽ thông báo qua email)</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Hãy gia nhập trên <a href=\"https://zalo.me/g/uhmmlm126\">nhóm Zalo</a> để nhận cập nhật liên kết tham gia.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Đăng ký tham gia</h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons is-layout-flex wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-button\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link wp-element-button\" href=\"https://forms.gle/4zxDZUb8jNLBFboY8\">Đăng ký tham gia</a></div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Đồng tổ chức</h2>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Hỗ trợ tổ chức sự kiện: <a href=\"https://minhduy.vn\">Minh Duy Solutions</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:79:\"https://vi.wordpress.org/2023/08/02/online-meetup-nha-trang-thang-08-2023/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"1\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:2;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:79:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:48:\"Recap: WordPress Meetup Hà Nội tháng 07/2023\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:80:\"https://vi.wordpress.org/2023/07/22/recap-wordpress-meetup-ha-noi-thang-07-2023/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s